title: Role of Honour for three Niuean First World War soldiers (New Zealand Government)
text: ( Source : New Zealand Government ) Three Niuean soldiers who served in the First World War will now be included in the New Zealand Roll of Honour and Commonwealth War Graves Commission records, Arts, Culture and Heritage Minister Maggie Barry
